{"lemma":"حَضَراتٌ","slug":"حَضَراتٌ","root":"ح.ض.ر","root_slug":"ح-ض-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-ض-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["adj","noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n8313","n8314","n8315","n8316"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D9%8E%D8%B6%D9%8E%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"presence"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"place with settled inhabitants"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"title of honor—Majesty, Highness, Excellency, Eminence"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of حَاضِر (ḥāḍir)","tags":["form-of","plural"]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"masculine plural of حَاضِر (ḥāḍir)","tags":["form-of","masculine","plural"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ħadˤ.ra/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n8313","headword_ar":"حَضْرَةٌ","root":"HDr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", originally an inf. n., signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Presence:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and afterwards applied to signify (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a place of presence"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as also the several forms occurring in the following phrases]. (MF.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kal~amotuhu","text_ar":"كَلَّمْتُهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bHiaDorap fulaAnK","text_ar":"بحَِضْرَة فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, * Msb,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAna *`lika baHaDoratihi","text_ar":"كَانَ ذٰلِكَ بَحَضْرَتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, * TA,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuDoratihi","text_ar":"حُضْرَتِهِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HDorataha","text_ar":"حضْرَتَهَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaDarihi","text_ar":"حَضَرِهِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Yaakoob, S, Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaDaritaha","text_ar":"حَضَرِتَهَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHoDarihi","text_ar":"مَحْضَرِهِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, Msb, K,) all syn. expressions, (K,) meaning (tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I spoke to him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that was"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"happened,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the presence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the place of presence, of such a one."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, Msb.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN Hasanu AlHiDorapi","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ حَسَنُ الحِضْرَةِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, A, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHuDorapi","text_ar":"الحُضْرَةِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is a person whose presence is attended by good."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaT~i A_inaA='aka biHaDorapi","text_ar":"غَطِّ اـِنَا=ءَكَ بِحَضْرَةِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al*~ubaAbi","text_ar":"الذُّبَابِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Cover thy vessel in the presence of the flies,"},{"kind":"text","text":"lest they taint it.] (A, TA. [Or perhaps this is a mistranscription, for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaHoDurohu Al*~ubaAbu","text_ar":"يَحْضُرْهُ الذُّبَابُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning, if thou do not,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the flies will come to it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and taint it.]) ―         -b2-  It is also applied as a title, by writers of letters and the like, to any great man with whom people are wont to be present; [and sometimes to God; and meaning (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"object of resort;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] as in the phrase,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHaDorapu AlEaAliyapu taA^omuru bika*aA","text_ar":"الحَضْرَةُ العَالِيَةُ تَاْمُرُ بِكَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The exalted object of resort commands such a thing"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (MF.) [It is similar to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AljanaAbu","text_ar":"الجَنَابُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but is generally considered as implying greater respect than the latter. It is often prefixed to the name of the person to whom it is applied, or to a pronoun: as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaDorapu fulaAnK","text_ar":"حَضْرَةُ فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The object of resort, such a one:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaDoratuka","text_ar":"حَضْرَتُكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The object of resort, thyself."},{"kind":"text","text":"] ―         -b3-  Also (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vicinity"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a thing, (T, A,) and of a man. (S. [So accord. to two copies of the S; but"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~ajuli","text_ar":"الرَّجُلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is there an evident mistranscription, for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~aHoli","text_ar":"الرَّحْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", “ of the house, ” or “ abode: ” see what follows.]) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kunotu biHaDorapi Ald~aAri","text_ar":"كُنْتُ بِحَضْرَةِ الدَّارِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I was in the vicinity of,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"near to, the house."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kun~aA biHaDorapi maA='K","text_ar":"كُنَّا بِحَضْرَةِ مَا=ءٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We were by a water."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA from a trad.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biHaDorapi AlmaA='i","text_ar":"بِحَضْرَةِ المَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"In the vicinity of,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"near to, the water."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) ―         -b4-  Also The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"finaA='","text_ar":"فِنَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajul","text_ar":"رَجُل"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S. [So accord. to two copies of the S; where it is said,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaDorapu Alr~ajuli qurobuhu wafinaAw^uhu","text_ar":"حَضْرَةُ الرَّجُلِ قُرْبُهُ وَفِنَاوُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": but the right reading is evidently"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~aHoli","text_ar":"الرَّحْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": so that the second of the two meanings thus explained is, The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"court,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"yard, in front,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extending from the sides,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a house, or an abode.])       -A2-  And (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Apparatus for building, such as baked bricks, and gypsum-plaster:"},{"kind":"text","text":"so in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamaEa AlHaDorapa","text_ar":"جَمَعَ الحَضْرَةَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yuriydu binaA='a daArK","text_ar":"يُرِيدُ بِنَا=ءَ دَارٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He collected the apparatus, such as the baked bricks, &c., desiring to build a house"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.)       -A3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaDarN","text_ar":"حَضَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","K","A","Msb","M","T"]},{"entry_id":"n8314","headword_ar":"حُضْرَةٌ","root":"HDr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaDorapN","text_ar":"حَضْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in five places."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n8315","headword_ar":"حِضْرَةٌ","root":"HDr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaDorapN","text_ar":"حَضْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in five places."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n8316","headword_ar":"حَضَرَةٌ","root":"HDr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaDorapN","text_ar":"حَضْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in five places."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}